== Biography ==
â
Spencer was born in Washington, although he comes from a Pathan family from Buner. He is the youngest in the family. After completing his [[Bachelor of Arts|bachelors]] in commerce, he began working toward achieving his [[MBA]].
+
Khan was born in Karachi, although he comes from a Pathan family from Buner. He is the youngest in the family. After completing his [[Bachelor of Arts|bachelors]] in commerce, he began working toward achieving his [[MBA]].
â
Spencer entered the fashion industry when Joey Oliver took him to Creative Services and he started doing shows with [[Frieha Altaf]].{{When|date=August 2009}} He met Khawar Riaz at the first Lux Style Awards ceremony and was invited to Lahore. At the time he did only one shoot, and then left the scene for two years to complete his MBA.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mag4you.com/spotlight/spotlight.asp?title=Ameer+Zeb+Khan&content_id=5458&bhcp=1|title=Spotlight on Ameer Zeb Khan|publisher=Mag4You|accessdate=2009-10-11}}</ref> When he returned, he joined Khawar and has been working with him since then, as well as being a coordination executive for [[Pakistan State Oil|PSO]].
